                </button>
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  <div class="accordion-description">
                    <p>More than just a mirror - The Brook Mirror is an architectural focal point designed for lasting beauty and unparalleled clarity. Its dynamic, bold asymmetry makes a statement in any room, from the entryway to the living room.</p>
                    <p>The robust 304-grade stainless steel frame in a refined Champagne Gold finish resists corrosion and moisture, making it equally suited to bathrooms as it is to bedrooms. Mountable vertically or horizontally for total flexibility.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
